channel.title: Refactored 317 client Attempts to JagGrab title.dat
channel.description:
Small problem with the refactored 317 client. [b]Sometimes[/b] when the client starts to load, it tries to JagGrab the file "title.dat", which will obviously not work, and it stops loading. Now this only happens once and a while, but apparently it is enough to annoy my players. :rolleyes:
Has anyone ever had this problem or know how to fix it? (And only people who know what the heck their talking about ;))
